Program Version 1.0 30/12/2015

General Usage Notes:

This is a game where you can improve your communication skills.

You can also learn how appropriately words can be placed in a sentence.

If you need a profound quote or insight for an upcoming speech, interview or whatever, try this.

If you don't like the first generated profundity, click again for a whole new one.

Just keep going until you find a quote that suits whatever the occasion requires. 
 
Click on generate and different sentences are provided.


